    <section class="- topic/section " xtrc="section:1;7:14" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:2;8:14" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Audio Hierarchy</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;9:10" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Audio in Lingua Workbench is organized in three levels:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol " xtrc="ol:1;10:11" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:1;11:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:1;11:16" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Source Audio</b> - The original uploaded file, organized by Drama → Season → Episode</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:2;12:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:2;12:16" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Audio Chunks</b> - Automatically created 5-minute segments of the source audio</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:3;13:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:3;13:16" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Audio Slices</b> - User-created regions within chunks for focused study</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
    
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrc="section:2;17:14" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:3;18:14" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">Processing Flow</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;19:10" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">When you upload an audio file:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol " xtrc="ol:2;20:11" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:4;21:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">The file is stored and associated with a drama/episode</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:5;22:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">It is automatically split into 5-minute chunks</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:6;23:13" xtrf="file:/C:/projects/lingua-workbench/docs/dita/topics/audio/c_audio_workflow.dita">You can then browse chunks and create slices for study</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
